description: King Tut's offers a mix of Egyptian and Mediterranean style cuisine. Known for their signature falafel made from all fresh ingredients, green herbs, onion and spices, that is then deep-fried until golden brown. They also serve Chicken Shwarma and Lamb Gyro with your choice of sauce, in a salad, over rice or on a sandwich! Overall offering great options for vegetarians and meat-lovers alike.
name: King Tut's Truck
